# =========================
# Streamlit Specific
# =========================
# 보안을 위해 API 키와 비밀번호가 포함된 secrets 파일은 반드시 제외해야 합니다.
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# =========================
# Python
# =========================
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# C extensions
*.so

# Distribution / packaging
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
share/python-wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
MANIFEST

# =========================
# Virtual Environments
# =========================
venv/
env/
.venv/
.env/
env.bak/
venv.bak/

# =========================
# IDEs and Editors
# =========================
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# =========================
# OS Generated Files
# =========================
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# =========================
# Data & Logs (선택 사항)
# =========================
# 데이터 파일이나 로그를 깃허브에 올리고 싶지 않다면 주석(#)을 해제하세요.
*.csv
*.json
*.xlsx
*.db
*.sqlite3
*.log